<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦٦:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {أَمَّا مَنِ اسْتَغْنَى <span class="c2">(٥)</span> فَأَنْتَ لَهُ تَصَدَّى <span class="c2">(٦)</span> وَمَا عَلَيْكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّى <span class="c2">(٧)</span> وَأَمَّا مَنْ جَاءَكَ يَسْعَى <span class="c2">(٨)</span> وَهُوَ يَخْشَى <span class="c2">(٩)</span> فَأَنْتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّى <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>} <span class="c4">[عبس: ٥ - ١٠]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{تَصَدَّى}</span>: <span class="c2">«تَغَافَلَ عَنْهُ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{تَلَهَّى}</span>: تَشَاغَلَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>